div.p:
Defense, in collaboration with the Department of State, would prepare a paper, by close of business April 25, 1974, addressing the following:
—What can we do to expedite present programs of military, economic, and drought assistance to Ethiopia;
—What additional assistance can we give over and above FY 1974 and FY 1975 programs;
—What items of military hardware we would be able and willing to sell to Ethiopia for cash.
